    "The generalization gap of only 7.5 percentage points indicates the model learns a robust skill rather than memorizing specific concept-vector mappings.Relation to Lindsey's Criteria.",
    "Lindsey defines introspective awareness via four criteria: accuracy, grounding, internality, and metacognitive representation.",
    "On the injected-thought detection task, our trained model satisfies:1.",
    "Accuracy: 85% correct identification on novel concepts (vs. ∼20% in Lindsey's best model).2.",
    "Grounding: 0% false positives across 60 control trials establishes causal dependence on actual injections.3."
